    <item>
      <title>印度中产阶级陷入困境，HDFC 银行和印度斯坦联合利华受到挤压</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/hdfc-bank-hindustan-unilever-squeezed-as-indian-middle-class-struggles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度工资下降和高通胀将影响 HDFC 银行有限公司、柯塔克马辛德拉银行有限公司和印度斯坦联合利华有限公司的盈利，因为这些银行正准备应对资产质量恶化，而消费品公司则面临着吝啬的客户问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/hdfc-bank-hindustan-unilever-squeezed-as-indian-middle-class-struggles</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 01:33:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
